These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  mechanic, bartender, journalist, accountant, scientist, analyst, architect
The people have 7 different hobbies: video-games, writing, dancing, drawing, magic-tricks, filmmaking, photography
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the architect##1
 2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the journalist##3
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is the mechanic##1
 5. the person who's hobby is writing is the accountant##1
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is in the middle##1
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the journalist is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
11. the mechanic is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
12. the journalist is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
13. the architect is on the right of the analyst##1
14. the scientist is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |    7    |
| Job   | scientist      | journalist      | analyst    | architect    | bartender | mechanic     | accountant     |
| Hobby   | drawing | magic-tricks | dancing | video-games | filmmaking   | photography | writing |

