.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, milk, almond-milk, lemonade, hot-chocolate, tea
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: marigold, balloon-flower, zinnia, daisy, dahlia, daffodil, bellflower
 1. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 2. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 3. the person who growsdahlia is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
 5. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who growsdahlia##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who growsdaffodil##1
10. the person drinking milk is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person drinking iced-tea##2
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
12. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left or far right##3
13. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |      5      |     6     |   7    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | milk | almond-milk | hot-chocolate   | tea | cola | lemonade |
| Flower           | dahlia | marigold          | daffodil    | balloon-flower | daisy     | zinnia      | bellflower    |

