.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-3::.
House: futuristic, farmhouse, victorian, art-deco, wooden, cottage, ranch-style
The people use 7 different means of transport: trike, ship, bike, van, helicopter, airplane, train
 1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
 3. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 4. the farmhouse house is between the cottage house and the art-deco house##2
 5. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the cottage house##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the ship is the futuristic house##1
10. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
11. the person driving the airplane is the ranch-style house##1
12. the person driving the helicopter is between the victorian house and the ranch-style house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |       5        |        6        |     7      |
| House   | art-deco        | farmhouse  | cottage | victorian | wooden           | ranch-style           | futuristic  |
| Transport    | trike | van | train   | bike    | helicopter | airplane | ship |

