 1. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
 2. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
 3. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4
 6. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
 7. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
 8. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
 9. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
10. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the game-smoker##1
11. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
12. the fonseca-smoker is on the far left##1
13. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4      |      5       |      6      |      7      |
| Cigar   | fonseca | alhambra    | bongani | bolivar | blend      | game | siglo |
| City     | marseilles  | colone | rome   | paris  | hamburg | london     | miami    |

