 1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
 5. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is the person watching comedy movies##1
 9. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4
10. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
11. the person watching comedy movies is in the middle##1
12. the person watching epic movies is the person who's birthday is in february##1
13. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
