 1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 4. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
 5. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 7. the person who likes green is in an even position##4
 8. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
10. the person who likes coral is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who likes apricot##2
11. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
12. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |    3     |   4   |    5    |       6       |      7      |
| Color   | brown     | apricot   | coral      | green | light-blue    | mauve | white |
| Sport       | biathlon | badminton | rowing | cricket  | volleyball | sailing     | climbing    |

