.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-19::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: video-games, writing, filmmaking, hiking, woodworking, board-games, traveling
There are 7 different favourite colors: chestnut, black, azure, writing, lilac, grey, fuchsia
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who likes grey##1
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
 3. the person who likes lilac is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 5. the person who likes lilac is in the middle##1
 6. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who likes azure##1
 9. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes black##1
10. the person who likes writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
11. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
13. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
14. the person who likes writing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |     5     |    6    |    7    |
| Hobby          | hiking  | writing | video-games     | traveling  | filmmaking | board-games    | woodworking  |
| Color   | writing | grey  | chestnut | lilac | black | fuchsia | azure |

