.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-20::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  mechanic, analyst, entrepreneur, dressmaker, pilot, accountant, lawyer
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: october, april, march, november, february, january, september
 1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 2. the mechanic is on the left or right of the pilot##3
 3. the pilot is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
 5. the dressmaker is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the dressmaker##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 8. the analyst is on the right of the pilot##1
 9. the accountant is in an odd position##4
10. the lawyer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
11. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
12. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |   5    |      6      |    7     |
| Job          | accountant   | entrepreneur | lawyer | mechanic | pilot | analyst | dressmaker |
| Birthday   | february | september      | january     | march  | november | october         | april    |

 